             <h1 class="h2"><a href="https://www.huckmag.com/perspectives/activism-2/the-fight-for-justice-for-chris-kaba-in-photos/" rel="bookmark" title="The fight for justice for Chris Kaba – in photos">The fight for justice for Chris Kaba – in photos</a></h1>
            <div class="post-subtitle">
    <h2>
        <a href="https://www.huckmag.com/perspectives/activism-2/the-fight-for-justice-for-chris-kaba-in-photos/" title="The fight for justice for Chris Kaba – in photos">Black lives matter</a>
    </h2>
</div><!-- post-subtitle -->
                    </div><!-- post-titles -->
    </header>
    
    <section class="entry-content clearfix">
